title: Former Facebook executive: 'It's making us sick'
text: Tim Kendall, CEO of moment and former Facebook executive, joins "Squawk Alley" to discuss why he thinks the social media platform needs more regulation.

title: Netflix, Facebook, Microsoft Among The Top Trending Stocks Rated Attractive
text: After three consecutive weeks of moving lower, the stock markets ended the week on a positive note on Friday. The deep learning algorithms at Q.ai have used Artificial Intelligence (“AI”) technology and rated some Trending Stocks this week.

title: Sheryl Sandberg On Facebook’s Role In Small Business Support And Voter Registration During The Pandemic
text: At Forbes’ first Small Business Summit held virtually on Friday, COO Sheryl Sandberg discussed how Facebook has “doubled down” on product launches for small businesses and how Congress can do more to help them survive coronavirus.
